VIVO Harvester
VIVO: Enabling National Networking of Scientists

Thanks for your interest in using the harvester. Below is a listing of resources for documentation and help.

Sourceforge Wiki:
http://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/vivo/index.php?title=Harvester_User_Guide
https://sourceforge.net/apps/mediawiki/vivo/index.php?title=Harvester
