Example scripts
The example-scripts directory contains example scripts for reference and demonstration. These are meant as a guide and template to follow for your own harvest.
	The xml configuration files found in our example-scripts/ folders document each parameter used (and some unused).
	
HELP Messages	
The Ðhelp message for each tool is always up-to-date on what parameters exist, but sparse on explaination
To see a help message, run <HarvesterInstallationDirectory>/bin/harvester-<toolName> --help
Example:
/usr/share/vivo/harvester/bin/harvester-databaseclone Ðhelp

Reporting bugs / researching existing bugs & workarounds
The VIVO JIRA Bug Tracker @ Cornell
http://issues.library.cornell.edu/browse/VIVOHARV